annotations.title: Coquito and Which Rum is Best? | How to Drink

textContent:
2 oz. Evaporated milk
15 oz. Coconut Cream
4 cinnamon stick
2 cloves
2 star anise
1 tsp vanilla
Grated nutmeg
10 oz rum [Don Q Gold]

Heat all but rum to simmer for about 10 minutes
Strain mixture into a bottle and let cool
Add rum now or single serving at 2:5 ratio rum to mix
